p: In the District Court at Montesano
Territory of Washington vs. Gus Beudjus &as}

The Grand Jury of Chehalis County having returned into this court on indictment against the defendant in the above named cause charging them with the crime of Malicious Mischief and it appearing to the court that said defendants are not in custody or under recognizance to appear and answer in this court, it is ordered that the clerk of this court issue a warrant for the arrest of said defendants forthwith
